Exactly as pictured
Rating

I love this case for several reasons. I got the emerald green and gold. It's really classy and the plastic is very glossy. The tight camera openings means that my red phone is completely hidden so no need to match your case to the color of the phone. The only downside is that with a rubberized case and the large metal area for the ring, it doesn't want to charge on a wireless charger. Easy to pop in and out of the case so I can still charge on my nightstand wireless charger but it would be nice if I didn't have to.

Review by Bethany Robertson

Posted on 4/20/23

Cute but only for a short time
Rating	
40%
Do not buy this. Trust me! I wanted to ignore the negative reviews and hope it would work at least for a couple months but it didn’t. It started chipping right away. The ring holder was too tight and first, then it was nice for a while, then it loosened completely and just dangled from my phone so I had to immediately replace it. Don’t waste your money.

Review by N Randall

Just plug the adapter in your device, let your Apple  equipment recognize the adapter for 3-5 sec before playing music. </p> <p class="a-spacing-base"> <span class="a-text-bold">Safe and Reliable</span> </p> <p class="a-spacing-base"> UGREEN 3.5mm plug to Lightning cable made from original Apple chips provides a secure and stable sound transmission. </p> </div>
